==Description==

The [[Image:Sketcher_CreateHexagon.svg|24px]] [[Sketcher_CreateHexagon|Sketcher CreateHexagon]] tool creates a hexagon. {{Version|1.0}}: This is the same tool as [[Sketcher_CreateRegularPolygon|Sketcher CreateRegularPolygon]] but with the number of sides preset to 6.

[[Image:SketcherCreateHexagonExample.png‎]]

==Usage==

See also: [[Sketcher_Workbench#Drawing_aids|Drawing aids]].

# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:Sketcher_CreateHexagon.svg|16px]] [[Sketcher_CreateHexagon|Hexagon]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Sketch → Geometries → [[Image:Sketcher_CreateHexagon.svg|16px]] Hexagon}} option from the menu.
#* Right-click in the [[3D_View|3D View]] and select the {{MenuCommand|[[Image:Sketcher_CreateHexagon.svg|16px]] Hexagon}} option from the context menu.
#* Use the keyboard shortcut: {{KEY|G}} then {{KEY|P}}, then {{KEY|6}}.
# For further steps see [[Sketcher_CreateRegularPolygon#Usage|Sketcher CreateRegularPolygon]].


